title: Person Of Interest || Feeling Good (Season 3)
author: Real Scorsese
comment: Another jewel in your crown!  Love your edits....they are long enough to get a sense of the scene.  So well one!  Choice of music is always perfect!  Well done once again!
Michael Bublé singing while John Reese is smacking the bad guys - that is something ;)
You know how I feel... I'm feeling good. It's a new day. It's a new video. And I'm feeling good.
description: I appreciate Michael Bublé, listening to his version of Nina Simone feel good I wanted to put on a humor side rather than an emotional side, to change a little. I hope you enjoy it as much as I enjoyed to mount this video, and laugh several times, feel free to share the Max
